The '''Finnish national under-21 football team''' is the [[national under-21 football team]] of [[Finland]]. The team qualified for the [[UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship]] final tournament in 2009.
==UEFA U-21 Championship Record== * '''[[1978 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1978]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 3 in qualification group. * '''[[1980 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1980]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 3 in qualification group. * '''[[1982 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1982]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 4th of 4 in qualification group. * '''[[1984 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1984]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 4 in qualification group. * '''[[1986 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1986]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 2nd of 4 in qualification group. * '''[[1988 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1988]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 4 in qualification group. * '''[[1990 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1990]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 4th of 4 in qualification group. * '''[[1992 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1992]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 4 in qualification group. * '''[[1994 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1994]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 6 in qualification group. * '''[[1996 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1996]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 2nd of 5 in qualification group. * '''[[1998 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|1998]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 4th of 6 in qualification group. * '''[[2000 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2000]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 5 in qualification group. * '''[[2002 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2002]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 4th of 5 in qualification group. * '''[[2004 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2004]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 5 in qualification group. * '''[[2006 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2006]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 5th of 7 in qualification group. * '''[[2007 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2007]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 3 in qualification group. * '''[[2009 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2009]]:''' '''Qualified'''. Finished 4th of 4 in Group B. * '''[[2011 UEFA European Under-21 Football Championship|2011]]:''' Did not qualify. Finished 3rd of 5 in qualification group.
